<F P=100> RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> Media Issues </F>
<H3> <TI>   ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI Publication Suspended 25 Jan </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2401204094 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1800 GMT 
24 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2401204094 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Radio Rossii Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tomorrow's issue of ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI will probably 
not be published. INTERFAX has learned that the publication of 
the newspaper was suspended because it has no money to pay for 
paper and printing. 
  The situation is explained by the fact that at the end of 
December the editorial staff took over the ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI 
from the Russian Government. However, the newspaper has not 
been registered yet and therefore cannot carry out independent 
financial transactions. 

</TEXT>

