<H3> <TI>   Replacement Troops Leave for Sarajevo </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2601213294 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1937 GMT 26 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2601213294 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow INTERFAX </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A transport aircraft with a group of Odessa military 
district troops took off from Nikolayev for Sarajevo. This is a 
second planeload of servicemen who will replace their comrades 
in the UN peace-keeping force in Bosnia-Herzegovina. 
  A spokesman for the Odessa military district told INTERFAX- 
Ukraine that a total of four such flights would be flown. 
Ukrainian women medics are flying for the first time to 
Sarajevo. 

</TEXT>

