<H3> <TI>   Commission Finds Crimean Presidential Elections Illegal </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2701093994 Kiev UNIAN in Ukrainian 0831 GMT 27 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2701093994 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UNIAN </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Kiev--A UNIAN correspondent has learned that a 
session of the Ukrainian Supreme Council's Legislation and 
Legality Commission on 26 January found that the presidential 
elections in the Republic of the Crimea, with their second round 
planned for 30 January, did not conform to Ukrainian law. The 
commission intends to make this conclusion known to parliament 
in the very near future. 

</TEXT>

