<H3> <TI>   Armenians Strive To Retake Positions </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC2601195694 Baku TURAN in English 1738 GMT 26 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2601195694 </F>
<F P=104>  Baku TURAN </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Baku (January 26) TURAN--Fighting in the northern 
sectors of the front in the vicinity of the city of Agdere 
(Mardakert) continues. According to information received by 
TURAN news agency in the executive apparatus of the Ter-Terskiy 
region, Armenian forces attempted to grasp the initiative. With 
this in mind, the Armenians launched an offensive this morning 
against positions the Azerbaijani forces retook yesterday in the 
vicinity of Agdere. 
  Fighting along the Kelbadzharskiy line of advance, where the 
Azeri units built concrete bunkers in the locations as they 
retake them. 

</TEXT>

