<H3> <TI>   Metallurgical Workers Demand Return to Ruble Zone </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PM2601160994 Moscow KOMSOMOLSKAYA PRAVDA in Russian 26 Jan 
94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> PM2601160994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KOMSOMOLSKAYA PRAVDA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Strikes in Kazakhstan"] </F>
  [Text] The situation in Ust-Kamenogorsk has deteriorated, 
The oblast's metallurgical workers have held a big rally by way 
of an ultimatum and demanded that the region return to the ruble 
zone. Major metallurgical enterprises have no money in their 
accounts and workers have not been paid for five months. To 
date metallurgical workers are owed over 35 million tenges. 
  Ten enterprises are standing idle. And 15 are on the verge 
of bankruptcy. The number of unemployed in the republic has 
doubled. 

</TEXT>

