<F P=102>  LD2601164894 Tallinn Radio Tallinn Network in Estonian 1800 
GMT 25 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2601164894 </F>
<F P=104>  Tallinn Radio Tallinn Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Estonian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] [passage omitted] The Estonian government decided 
to close its trade mission in Ukraine. The prime minister's 
reason for this is the fact that the trade mission was set up in 
Ukraine a long time ago and has failed to fulfill the goals set 
for it. Furthermore, our trade mission has not yet been accepted 
in Ukraine to the required degree. Now that there is also an 
Estonian Embassy in Kiev, the trade mission's primary functions 
can be met through the embassy. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

