Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tallinn, Jan 26, BNS -- The Estonian Economics 
Ministry in its activity abides by a government ruling from Oct. 
25, 1993, which says the country's two major distilleries are to 
remain in state ownership, Economics Minister Toivo Jurgenson 
told BNS. 
