<F P=100> INTERREGIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Defense Ministers End Meeting </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2801103694 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 0900 GMT 
28 Jan 94 </F>

