Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Yerevan, January 27 (SNARK)--Tomorrow Vladimir 
Kazimirov, the ambassador for special missions and the special 
envoy of Russian president, will leave for the zone of Karabakh 
conflict. SNARK was informed about it by diplomatic sources. 
  It is supposed that he will visit Yerevan, Baku, Stepanakert 
where he will meet with the leaders of Armenia, Azerbaijan, 
