  [Excerpts] Estonia's Government appointed new Finance 
Minister Heiki Kranich the country's representative at the 
boards of governors of the European Bank for Development and 
Reconstruction (EBRD) and the World Bank. [passage omitted] 
  Kranich was also appointed Estonian coordinator at economic 
cooperation programmes with the Commission of the European 
Communities and G-24. 

