Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [POSTFACTUM report under the "In Brief" rubric] </F>
  [Text] Novosibirsk -- Vasiliy Lipitskiy, 
Novosibirsk-elected State Duma deputy, and leader of the "Free 
Russia" People's Party, intends to press for parliament to pass 
