<H3> <TI>   Kravchuk Not Likely To Interfere in Crimea `Yet' </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2701154594 Kiev UNIAR in Ukrainian 1210 GMT 27 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2701154594 </F>
